column1: This table shows the differential expression results for genes with absolute log2FC > 1.5 and adjusted p-value < 0.05 when comparing Lmx1a_E1 and Sox3U3 samples (Lmx1a_E1 - Sox3U3)
Normalised count: read counts adjusted for library size
pvalue: unadjusted pvalue for differential expression test between Lmx1a_E1 and Sox3U3 samples
padj: pvalue for differential expression test between Lmx1a_E1 and Sox3U3 samples - adjusted for multiple testing (Benjamini and Hochberg)
